#Financial Performance Report (Past 5 Years): Apple vs Microsoft vs Alphabet 

Companies: Apple(AAPL), Microsoft(MSFT), Alphabet(GOOG)
Window: Last 5 year fiscal years available in the dataset
Objectives: Compare growth, profitability, cash generation, and balance-sheet strength across the three firms.

# Questions this notebook answers 
1.Which company grew fastest (Revenue, NetIncome, FCF)?
2.Which company generates the best profitability (Margins)?
3.Which company looks safest from a balance-sheet view (Net cash, leverage)?

